ğŸ‘‰ Lists use square brackets []

2ï¸âƒ£ Accessing List Elements (Indexing)
numbers = [10, 20, 30, 40]

print(numbers[0])   # 10
print(numbers[2])   # 30
print(numbers[-1])  # 40

3ï¸âƒ£ List Slicing
numbers = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]

print(numbers[1:4])   # [20, 30, 40]
print(numbers[:3])    # [10, 20, 30]

4ï¸âƒ£ Modify List
